---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
import crossword2021Thumb from "../assets/crossword_2021_thumb.jpg";
import crossword2021Pdf from "../assets/crossword_2021.pdf";
import qrb2004 from "../assets/qrb_2004.gif";
import qrb2021 from "../assets/qrb_2021.jpg";
import qrb2026 from "../assets/qrb_2026.jpg";

const pageTitle = "About";
---

<BaseLayout pageTitle={pageTitle}>
  <div class="container max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 md:px-0">
    <div class="mt-10 md:text-md text-base">
      <div class="space-y-4 md:grid md:grid-cols-3 md:gap-6 md:items-start md:space-y-0">
      <p class="md:col-span-2">
        The Quadraphonic Rock Block started in 2004 in Kirksville, Missouri. My first attempt at college was at a weird, small, fun little school called Truman State University in the middle of absolutely nowhere. I had a friend online who went there and I applied on a whim, and not knowing what else to do with my life, decided to try my luck at Truman after high school. Four thousand panic attacks later I retreated back home to Arizona, but not before (a) meeting the woman who would become both a great friend and the mother of my children, and (b) getting a radio show on Dobson Radio, a tiny little station run out of my dorm. I named it the Quadraphonic Rock Bloc (no k for cool reasons) because it sounded awesome, and I spent most of my shows playing the Smiths and Mogwai and Neutral Milk Hotel and generally broadcasting my angst to the three people who were able to receive our tiny little signal. Those playlists are lost to time but trust me, that's for the best.
      </p>
      <a
        href={qrb2004.src}
        target="_blank"
        rel="noopener noreferrer"
        class="group relative hidden overflow-hidden md:block md:col-span-1 md:row-span-2 md:justify-self-end md:self-start"
      >
        <img
          src={qrb2004.src}
          alt="Quadraphonic Rock Block flyer from 2004"
          class="w-full transition duration-200 md:w-full md:group-hover:brightness-75 md:group-hover:saturate-150 md:group-hover:hue-rotate-180"
        />
        <span class="absolute top-2 left-2 bg-blue-600/85 px-2 py-1 text-xs font-semibold text-white opacity-100 transition duration-200 md:opacity-0 md:group-hover:opacity-100">
          QRB's first flyer from 2004 &lt;3
        </span>
      </a>
      </div>

      <div class="mt-4 flow-root">
      <div class="hidden md:block md:float-left md:w-1/3 md:mr-6 mb-4 space-y-4">
        <a
          href={crossword2021Pdf}
          target="_blank"
          rel="noopener noreferrer"
          class="group relative block overflow-hidden"
        >
          <img
            src={crossword2021Thumb.src}
            alt="KUCR crossword from 2021"
            class="w-full transition duration-200 md:group-hover:brightness-75 md:group-hover:saturate-150 md:group-hover:hue-rotate-180"
          />
          <span class="absolute top-2 left-2 bg-blue-600/85 px-2 py-1 text-xs font-semibold text-white opacity-100 transition duration-200 md:opacity-0 md:group-hover:opacity-100">
            Crossword for KUCR's quaranzine
          </span>
        </a>
        <a
          href={qrb2021.src}
          target="_blank"
          rel="noopener noreferrer"
          class="group relative block overflow-hidden"
        >
          <img
            src={qrb2021.src}
            alt="Quadraphonic Rock Block image from 2021"
            class="w-full transition duration-200 md:group-hover:brightness-75 md:group-hover:saturate-150 md:group-hover:hue-rotate-180"
          />
          <span class="absolute top-2 left-2 bg-blue-600/85 px-2 py-1 text-xs font-semibold text-white opacity-100 transition duration-200 md:opacity-0 md:group-hover:opacity-100">
            Ad for KUCR's quaranzine
          </span>
        </a>
      </div>
      <p>
        In 2021, I got the chance to join the genuinely wonderful people at KUCR and the Quadraphonic Rock Block came back to life, with an added "k" at the end of "Bloc" because I am now 40. It remains the highlight of my Fridays, and I feel truly fortunate to have the chance to share music that I love with people I don't know. I hope you hear something you like ❤️ And get in touch if you ever feel the urge!
      </p>
      <a
        href={qrb2026.src}
        target="_blank"
        rel="noopener noreferrer"
        class="group relative mt-4 block overflow-hidden md:ml-[calc(33.333333%+1.5rem)] md:w-[calc(66.666667%-1.5rem)]"
      >
        <img
          src={qrb2026.src}
          alt="Quadraphonic Rock Block image from 2026"
          class="w-full transition duration-200 md:group-hover:brightness-75 md:group-hover:saturate-150 md:group-hover:hue-rotate-180"
        />
        <span class="absolute top-2 left-2 bg-blue-600/85 px-2 py-1 text-xs font-semibold text-white opacity-100 transition duration-200 md:opacity-0 md:group-hover:opacity-100">
          The QRB of today!
        </span>
      </a>
      <div class="block md:hidden mt-4 space-y-4">
        <a
          href={qrb2004.src}
          target="_blank"
          rel="noopener noreferrer"
          class="group relative block overflow-hidden"
        >
          <img
            src={qrb2004.src}
            alt="Quadraphonic Rock Block flyer from 2004"
            class="w-full transition duration-200 md:group-hover:brightness-75 md:group-hover:saturate-150 md:group-hover:hue-rotate-180"
          />
          <span class="absolute top-2 left-2 bg-blue-600/85 px-2 py-1 text-xs font-semibold text-white opacity-100 transition duration-200 md:opacity-0 md:group-hover:opacity-100">
            QRB's first flyer from 2004 &lt;3
          </span>
        </a>
        <a
          href={crossword2021Pdf}
          target="_blank"
          rel="noopener noreferrer"
          class="group relative block overflow-hidden"
        >
          <img
            src={crossword2021Thumb.src}
            alt="KUCR crossword from 2021"
            class="w-full transition duration-200 md:group-hover:brightness-75 md:group-hover:saturate-150 md:group-hover:hue-rotate-180"
          />
          <span class="absolute top-2 left-2 bg-blue-600/85 px-2 py-1 text-xs font-semibold text-white opacity-100 transition duration-200 md:opacity-0 md:group-hover:opacity-100">
            Crossword for KUCR's quaranzine
          </span>
        </a>
        <a
          href={qrb2021.src}
          target="_blank"
          rel="noopener noreferrer"
          class="group relative block overflow-hidden"
        >
          <img
            src={qrb2021.src}
            alt="Quadraphonic Rock Block image from 2021"
            class="w-full transition duration-200 md:group-hover:brightness-75 md:group-hover:saturate-150 md:group-hover:hue-rotate-180"
          />
          <span class="absolute top-2 left-2 bg-blue-600/85 px-2 py-1 text-xs font-semibold text-white opacity-100 transition duration-200 md:opacity-0 md:group-hover:opacity-100">
            Ad for KUCR's quaranzine
          </span>
        </a>
      </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>